{"ID":"20220906204309-i2hqixy","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220906204309-i2hqixy","title":"h-1cdn","type":"doc","updated":"20220906204309"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204310-39a0n4d","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20220906204310-39a0n4d","updated":"20220906204310"}},{"ID":"20220906204311-5mhefhy","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204311-5mhefhy","updated":"20220906204311"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"8.2 CDN(内容分发网络)","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204312-45keffc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204312-45keffc","updated":"20220906204312"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是 CDN ？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204313-9qi6tam","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204313-9qi6tam","updated":"20220906204313"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"CDN"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 全称是 Content Delivery Network/Content Distribution Network，翻译过的意思是 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容分发网络"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204314-f7uqb67","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204314-f7uqb67","updated":"20220906204314"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们可以将内容分发网络拆开来看：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204315-6lovq91","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204315-6lovq91","updated":"20220906204315"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204316-qqi64rd","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204316-qqi64rd","updated":"20220906204316"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204317-wo687dw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204317-wo687dw","updated":"20220906204317"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"内容 ：指的是静态资源比如图片、视频、文档、JS、CSS、HTML。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204318-wdedbmc","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204318-wdedbmc","updated":"20220906204318"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204319-4anfak9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204319-4anfak9","updated":"20220906204319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分发网络 ：指的是将这些静态资源分发到位于多个不同的地理位置机房中的服务器上，这样，就可以实现静态资源的就近访问比如北京的用户直接访问北京机房的数据。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204320-hz105qr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204320-hz105qr","updated":"20220906204320"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"所以，简单来说，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"CDN 就是将静态资源分发到多个不同的地方以实现就近访问，进而加快静态资源的访问速度，减轻服务器以及带宽的负担。"}]},{"ID":"20220906204321-3h2pk0d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204321-3h2pk0d","updated":"20220906204321"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类似于京东建立的庞大的仓储运输体系，京东物流在全国拥有非常多的仓库，仓储网络几乎覆盖全国所有区县。这样的话，用户下单的第一时间，商品就从距离用户最近的仓库，直接发往对应的配送站，再由京东小哥送到你家。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204322-fc7ssub","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204322-fc7ssub","updated":"20220906204322"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"京东仓配系统","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/high-performance/cdn/jingdong-wuliu-cangpei.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204323-evavo9m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204323-evavo9m","updated":"20220906204323"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你可以将 CDN 看作是服务上一层的特殊缓存服务，分布在全国各地，主要用来处理静态资源的请求。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204324-l75gy91","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204324-l75gy91","updated":"20220906204324"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"CDN 简易示意图","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/high-performance/cdn/cdn-101.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204325-t1pjta5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204325-t1pjta5","updated":"20220906204325"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们经常拿全站加速和内容分发网络做对比，不要把两者搞混了！全站加速（不同云服务商叫法不同，腾讯云叫 ECDN、阿里云叫 DCDN）既可以加速静态资源又可以加速动态资源，内容分发网络（CDN）主要针对的是 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"静态资源"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204326-888wk9c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204326-888wk9c","updated":"20220906204326"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"阿里云文档：https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/64836.html","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/high-performance/cdn/cdn-aliyun-dcdn.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204327-7yzhzks","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204327-7yzhzks","updated":"20220906204327"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"绝大部分公司都会在项目开发中交使用 CDN 服务，但很少会有自建 CDN 服务的公司。基于成本、稳定性和易用性考虑，建议直接选择专业的云厂商（比如阿里云、腾讯云、华为云、青云）或者 CDN 厂商（比如网宿、蓝汛）提供的开箱即用的 CDN 服务。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204328-tj32o33","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204328-tj32o33","updated":"20220906204328"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"很多朋友可能要问了：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"既然是就近访问，为什么不直接将服务部署在多个不同的地方呢？"}]},{"ID":"20220906204329-th2kzn8","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204329-th2kzn8","updated":"20220906204329"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204330-0vggpus","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204330-0vggpus","updated":"20220906204330"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204331-rjiir1o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204331-rjiir1o","updated":"20220906204331"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"成本太高，需要部署多份相同的服务。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204332-v2js6a0","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204332-v2js6a0","updated":"20220906204332"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204333-zhu5z18","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204333-zhu5z18","updated":"20220906204333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态资源通常占用空间比较大且经常会被访问到，如果直接使用服务器或者缓存来处理静态资源请求的话，对系统资源消耗非常大，可能会影响到系统其他服务的正常运行。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204334-anxstbu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204334-anxstbu","updated":"20220906204334"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"同一个服务在在多个不同的地方部署多份（比如同城灾备、异地灾备、同城多活、异地多活）是为了实现系统的高可用而不是就近访问。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204335-ukx3h2i","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204335-ukx3h2i","updated":"20220906204335"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CDN 工作原理是什么？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204336-yqveium","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204336-yqveium","updated":"20220906204336"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"搞懂下面 3 个问题也就搞懂了 CDN 的工作原理：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204337-1cigtuw","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204337-1cigtuw","updated":"20220906204337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204338-x2nslew","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204338-x2nslew","updated":"20220906204338"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204339-tks5276","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204339-tks5276","updated":"20220906204339"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态资源是如何被缓存到 CDN 节点中的？","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204340-gp1plhs","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204340-gp1plhs","updated":"20220906204340"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204341-pycgmda","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204341-pycgmda","updated":"20220906204341"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何找到最合适的 CDN 节点？","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204342-dx9j1tb","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mw==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204342-dx9j1tb","updated":"20220906204342"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204343-nxctv7s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204343-nxctv7s","updated":"20220906204343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何防止静态资源被盗用？","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204344-xbclj6t","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204344-xbclj6t","updated":"20220906204344"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态资源是如何被缓存到 CDN 节点中的？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204345-hii3jo5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204345-hii3jo5","updated":"20220906204345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你可以通过预热的方式将源站的资源同步到 CDN 的节点中。这样的话，用户首次请求资源可以直接从 CDN 节点中取，无需回源。这样可以降低源站压力，提升用户体验。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204346-mtxe113","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204346-mtxe113","updated":"20220906204346"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果不预热的话，你访问的资源可能不再 CDN 节点中，这个时候 CDN 节点将请求源站获取资源，这个过程是大家经常说的 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"回源"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204347-d0h7p05","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204347-d0h7p05","updated":"20220906204347"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"命中率"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"回源率"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是衡量 CDN 服务质量两个重要指标。命中率越高越好，回源率越低越好。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204348-b85w8cz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204348-b85w8cz","updated":"20220906204348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果资源有更新的话，你也可以对其 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"刷新"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ，删除 CDN 节点上缓存的资源，当用户访问对应的资源时直接回源获取最新的资源，并重新缓存。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204349-7wmowg4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204349-7wmowg4","updated":"20220906204349"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何找到最合适的 CDN 节点？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204350-oxo9q5p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204350-oxo9q5p","updated":"20220906204350"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"GSLB （Global Server Load Balance，全局负载均衡）是 CDN 的大脑，负责多个 CDN 节点之间相互协作，最常用的是基于 DNS 的 GSLB。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204351-cg6buye","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204351-cg6buye","updated":"20220906204351"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CDN 会通过 GSLB 找到最合适的 CDN 节点，更具体点来说是下面这样的：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204352-gxqt0mv","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204352-gxqt0mv","updated":"20220906204352"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204353-simweck","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204353-simweck","updated":"20220906204353"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204354-b8yaquq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204354-b8yaquq","updated":"20220906204354"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"浏览器向 DNS 服务器发送域名请求；","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204355-kjhv5k5","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204355-kjhv5k5","updated":"20220906204355"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204356-qy5ufri","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204356-qy5ufri","updated":"20220906204356"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"DNS 服务器向根据 CNAME( Canonical Name ) 别名记录向 GSLB 发送请求；","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204357-g4rztve","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mw==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204357-g4rztve","updated":"20220906204357"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204358-zymh23d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204358-zymh23d","updated":"20220906204358"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"GSLB 返回性能最好（通常距离请求地址最近）的 CDN 节点（边缘服务器，真正缓存内容的地方）的地址给浏览器；","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204359-41i0qc0","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NA==","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204359-41i0qc0","updated":"20220906204359"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204360-m4xdn4v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204360-m4xdn4v","updated":"20220906204360"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"浏览器直接访问指定的 CDN 节点。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204361-5ki48ck","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204361-5ki48ck","updated":"20220906204361"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"CDN 原理示意图","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/high-performance/cdn/cdn-overview.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204362-qyiydq9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204362-qyiydq9","updated":"20220906204362"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为了方便理解，上图其实做了一点简化。GSLB 内部可以看作是 CDN 专用 DNS 服务器和负载均衡系统组合。CDN 专用 DNS 服务器会返回负载均衡系统 IP 地址给浏览器，浏览器使用 IP 地址请求负载均衡系统进而找到对应的 CDN 节点。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204363-hc71apk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204363-hc71apk","updated":"20220906204363"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"GSLB 是如何选择出最合适的 CDN 节点呢？"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" GSLB 会根据请求的 IP 地址、CDN 节点状态（比如负载情况、性能、响应时间、带宽）等指标来综合判断具体返回哪一个 CDN 节点的地址。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204364-rmdlb6i","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204364-rmdlb6i","updated":"20220906204364"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何防止资源被盗刷？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204365-up5fedh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204365-up5fedh","updated":"20220906204365"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果我们的资源被其他用户或者网站非法盗刷的话，将会是一笔不小的开支。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204366-y05o2rd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204366-y05o2rd","updated":"20220906204366"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解决这个问题最常用最简单的办法设置 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Referer 防盗链"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，具体来说就是根据 HTTP 请求的头信息里面的 Referer 字段对请求进行限制。我们可以通过 Referer 字段获取到当前请求页面的来源页面的网站地址，这样我们就能确定请求是否来自合法的网站。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204367-cr6xw9g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204367-cr6xw9g","updated":"20220906204367"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CDN 服务提供商几乎都提供了这种比较基础的防盗链机制。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204368-cyuls70","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204368-cyuls70","updated":"20220906204368"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"腾讯云 CDN Referer 防盗链配置","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/high-performance/cdn/cnd-tencent-cloud-anti-theft.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204369-tw57uys","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204369-tw57uys","updated":"20220906204369"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不过，如果站点的防盗链配置允许 Referer 为空的话，通过隐藏 Referer，可以直接绕开防盗链。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204370-4himn1a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204370-4himn1a","updated":"20220906204370"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"通常情况下，我们会配合其他机制来确保静态资源被盗用，一种常用的机制是 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"时间戳防盗链"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。相比之下，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"时间戳防盗链"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的安全性更强一些。时间戳防盗链加密的 URL 具有时效性，过期之后就无法再被允许访问。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204371-p8clbis","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204371-p8clbis","updated":"20220906204371"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间戳防盗链的 URL 通常会有两个参数一个是签名字符串，一个是过期时间。签名字符串一般是通过对用户设定的加密字符串、请求路径、过期时间通过 MD5 哈希算法取哈希的方式获得。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204372-ftfxyvt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204372-ftfxyvt","updated":"20220906204372"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间戳防盗链 URL 示例：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204373-95vp4u7","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906204373-95vp4u7","updated":"20220906204373"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"http://cdn.wangsu.com/4/123.mp3? wsSecret=79aead3bd7b5db4adeffb93a010298b5\u0026wsTime=1601026312\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204374-xr3yqls","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204374-xr3yqls","updated":"20220906204374"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204375-8b5q33x","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204375-8b5q33x","updated":"20220906204375"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204376-9qm8nef","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204376-9qm8nef","updated":"20220906204376"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"wsSecret"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：签名字符串。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204377-r91d4hs","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204377-r91d4hs","updated":"20220906204377"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204378-e7cizpv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204378-e7cizpv","updated":"20220906204378"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"wsTime"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 过期时间。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204379-cee5oob","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204379-cee5oob","updated":"20220906204379"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/high-performance/cdn/timestamp-anti-theft.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204380-nxuut6c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204380-nxuut6c","updated":"20220906204380"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间戳防盗链的实现也比较简单，并且可靠性较高，推荐使用。并且，绝大部分 CDN 服务提供商都提供了开箱即用的时间戳防盗链机制。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204381-uohbqoz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204381-uohbqoz","updated":"20220906204381"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"七牛云时间戳防盗链配置","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/high-performance/cdn/qiniuyun-timestamp-anti-theft.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204382-fc1y12w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204382-fc1y12w","updated":"20220906204382"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"除了 Referer 防盗链和时间戳防盗链之外，你还可以 IP 黑白名单配置、IP 访问限频配置等机制来防盗刷。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204383-d3kg01t","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204383-d3kg01t","updated":"20220906204383"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总结","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204384-xafwi2a","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204384-xafwi2a","updated":"20220906204384"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204385-kaa387r","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204385-kaa387r","updated":"20220906204385"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204386-28i7qyh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204386-28i7qyh","updated":"20220906204386"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CDN 就是将静态资源分发到多个不同的地方以实现就近访问，进而加快静态资源的访问速度，减轻服务器以及带宽的负担。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204387-dtiw4e1","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204387-dtiw4e1","updated":"20220906204387"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204388-5kfezop","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204388-5kfezop","updated":"20220906204388"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"基于成本、稳定性和易用性考虑，建议直接选择专业的云厂商（比如阿里云、腾讯云、华为云、青云）或者 CDN 厂商（比如网宿、蓝汛）提供的开箱即用的 CDN 服务。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204389-hweomm2","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204389-hweomm2","updated":"20220906204389"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204390-35dxr6b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204390-35dxr6b","updated":"20220906204390"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"GSLB （Global Server Load Balance，全局负载均衡）是 CDN 的大脑，负责多个 CDN 节点之间相互协作，最常用的是基于 DNS 的 GSLB。CDN 会通过 GSLB 找到最合适的 CDN 节点。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204391-bxijuha","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204391-bxijuha","updated":"20220906204391"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204392-lcx1j0f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204392-lcx1j0f","updated":"20220906204392"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为了防止静态资源被盗用，我们可以利用 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Referer 防盗链"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" + ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"时间戳防盗链"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204393-j2958hh","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204393-j2958hh","updated":"20220906204393"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"参考","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204394-wmj8ooe","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204394-wmj8ooe","updated":"20220906204394"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204395-grngt0q","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204395-grngt0q","updated":"20220906204395"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204396-3kg3h5u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204396-3kg3h5u","updated":"20220906204396"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间戳防盗链 - 七牛云 CDN：https://developer.qiniu.com/fusion/kb/1670/timestamp-hotlinking-prevention","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204397-0ogbmz6","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204397-0ogbmz6","updated":"20220906204397"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204398-b63nu7c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204398-b63nu7c","updated":"20220906204398"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CDN 是个啥玩意？一文说个明白：https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Pp0C8ALUXsmYCUkM5QnkQw","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204399-dp3jq4r","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204399-dp3jq4r","updated":"20220906204399"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204400-tgi5khi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204400-tgi5khi","updated":"20220906204400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《透视 HTTP 协议》- 37 | CDN：加速我们的网络服务：http://gk.link/a/11yOG","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]}]}